{
  "stem": "294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, I went in November of 1937, I went to Vienna to-- to-- I was supposed to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the only thing-- I don't know why my mother insisted that I go to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I hardly spoke German, so I had to improve my German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I enrolled already in medical school, and then I had to work hard on improving my German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in March of 1938, Austria was annexed to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And by coincidence, our whole group of Polish students were supposed to go back to Poland for Easter vacation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't know whether we will come back or not, because we witnessed the March of the Germans on March 13th-- 11 or 13th-- I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- not knowing anything-- I had a date with a friend on Opernplatz, in Vienna, which is the center of the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went there, and I saw the parade of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I saw how the Austrians were throwing flowers under their feet, and the enthusiasm of the local population with the arrival of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So no one can tell me that Austria was occupied by Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was done very willingly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the first--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The danger.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you see, being-- in 1938, I was-- I was 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when I came back home, I should have warned my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father died before the war, in 1934.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was an only child, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I should have warned my mother, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we never expected that something like this could happen to our country-- to Poland, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We believed in our army, and we thought that our cavalry can defeat the German tanks, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was naive-- very naive.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
